武汉被感染护士康复后返岗，隔离前曾给家人留“遗书”。
Wuhan after the recovery of infected nurses back to work, isolation before the family left "wills."
刘名洋。
Liu Mingyang.
新京报                      。
Beijing News.
新京报。
Beijing News.
